title: ISldWorks.GetBatchUploadedFilesInfo
description: Gets the files uploaded to 3DEXPERIENCE during a batch process.
signature:
System.Boolean GetBatchUploadedFilesInfo( 
   out System.Object
ProcessedFileNames
,
   out System.Object
NonProcessedFileNames
,
   out System.Object
FailedFileNames
)

parameters.name: FailedFileNames
parameters.description: Array of file names that failed to upload

returns: True if retrieval successful, false if not
remarks:
This method is valid only for
SOLIDWORKS Design Augmented
.
Before using this method, call
ISldWorks::RunBatchSaveProcess
.
